{
  "stem": "24515.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Number one, my brother and I were obviously spoiled children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean we had, you know-- we had a great deal going for us, see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then my parents-- in my opinion wrongly-- but my parents were determined that we should be protected from everything as far as possible, as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So no, there wasn't much discussion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, nothing really firm or really definite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more or less accepted-- it was understood-- that my brother and I would go to high school and probably this humanistic gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we'd probably go to university somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I myself, as a kid, wasn't aware-- averse to becoming a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you know, I saw my father doing very nicely, thank you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But you see-- OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hitler was in power.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, I was-- it was 1933 that I went to high school as Hitler had just come to power.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, look, wouldn't-- don't you think that with things being as they are, perhaps I should go into a school a little more practical a little more definite, you know, specific, since we may wish to emigrate, than this humanistic stuff.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father said, A, he was very pleased that I thought along those lines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "B, he thought that what I said made sense.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "However, his own experience was that the humanistic education was the best foundation for pretty much anything you want to be, whether you're going to be a shoemaker or a lawyer or a plumber or an industrial worker.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He felt that the humanistic background was the most efficient.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I myself found it was so, for at least for a guy like me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
